Package: lightcontrol
Section: main
Priority: optional
Version: 1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Ricardo Lima de Almeida <ricklimadealmeida@protonmail.com>
Description: Light Control
 This package provides the Light Control, which allows users to configure the Backlight / Brightness level and the temperature color of the display.
Homepage: https://sourceforge.net/projects/pin-linux-os/
Depends: python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-gtk-3.0
